aeReportHasWorkflowOnActiveReports

public boolean aeReportHasWorkflowOnActiveReports(ExpeditedAdverseEventReport aeReport)
This method will return true if the dataCollection (aeReport) has workflow enabled on any active reports. Reports with status other than (Withdrawn, Replaced or Amended) are considered to be active reports. In caAERS context even reports with status 'Completed' is considered to be inactive reports.

Parameters:
aeReport - the ae report
Returns:
true, if successful
